properties.description: This 300 mm underground pipeline is connected to the Loya Weyala District 9 reservoir, merged with the LoyaWeyala_1 Borewell and leading to the Water supply scheme in the mentioned area.
This is the main pipeline leading to the Reservoir, joined by the main pipe from the LoyaWeyala_2 Borewell, together feeding the main (12 Inches) pipeline.
It is the main pipeline that is used to feed the reservoir and to supply water to the water supply scheme.
